### Vote on a question (upvote)
POST https://localhost:7003/api/votes/vote
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "questionId": "12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789012",
  "userId": "87654321-4321-4321-4321-210987654321",
  "voteType": 1
}

### Vote on a question (downvote)
POST https://localhost:7003/api/votes/vote
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "questionId": "12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789012",
  "userId": "87654321-4321-4321-4321-210987654321",
  "voteType": -1
}

### Change vote from upvote to downvote
PUT https://localhost:7003/api/votes/change
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "questionId": "12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789012",
  "userId": "87654321-4321-4321-4321-210987654321",
  "newVoteType": -1
}

### Remove vote (set to neutral)
DELETE https://localhost:7003/api/votes/remove
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "questionId": "12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789012",
  "userId": "87654321-4321-4321-4321-210987654321"
}

### Get user's vote for a specific question
GET https://localhost:7003/api/votes/user/12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789012/87654321-4321-4321-4321-210987654321

### Get vote summary for a question (without user context)
GET https://localhost:7003/api/votes/summary/12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789012

### Get vote summary for a question (with user context)
GET https://localhost:7003/api/votes/summary/12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789012?userId=87654321-4321-4321-4321-210987654321

### Get all votes for a question
GET https://localhost:7003/api/votes/question/12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789012

